          "comment": "2-2 when blinkered in 1m5f races on good ground, the latter a Listed race at Navan",
          "spotlight": "Made his debut less than six weeks ago but is now unbeaten in two 1m5f races on good ground, the latter a Listed race at Navan in which he gradually asserted in the last 2f to score by 3l as 6-4 favourite; blinkered in both; this race demands plenty more and some of the others look more stoutly bred but his ceiling has not yet been revealed.",
