          "comment": "Overall record of 4-9 and went close in Group 2 at the Curragh latest; in the mix",
          "spotlight": "Overall record of 4-9 and she's made more progress this season, with Group 3 win at the Curragh (1m, good) in April and a close second in Group 2 there last month; went down fighting last time behind 5-4 favourite who has had plenty of success in top-level events; respected.",
