          "comment": "Retains plenty of ability aged nine but he's on a 21-race losing sequence",
          "spotlight": "Finished eighth in this event in 2022; couple of second-place finishes at Newmarket this term show that he retains plenty of ability aged nine; however, he's on a 21-race losing sequence and can be opposed.",
