              "distance_f": "9",
              "distance_y": "1980",
              "quote": "As I said before the race, Toimy Son is in the form of his life. It was not ideal today with the ground becoming a bit tacky, and he is probably better at a mile, but he's run another stormer. He's in the Balmoral Handicap on Champions Day and that's where we'll go with him - David Menuisier, trainer."
