          "comment": "Dual hurdle winner for James Owen last season but has a point to prove on stable debut",
          "spotlight": "Dual hurdle winner for James Owen last season, latterly in Stratford seller (2m2f, good) in March; changed hands for \u00a35,500 after a disappointing run last month and has a point to prove on stable debut.",
