              "distance_f": "16",
              "distance_y": "3523",
              "quote": "It was a bad race and well found by the trainer as the 3yos got a big weight allowance. G'Day Aussie jumped well but hopefully the handicapper won't overreact as it was not a good race - Brian Hughes, jockey."
